OL,3,CThermal imaging drone used to count
OL,4,Cseals in Jersey
OL,6,FA Jersey charity has begun using a
OL,7,Fthermal imaging drone to accurately
OL,8,Fcount the number of grey seals in the
OL,9,Fisland's waters.
OL,11,FPreviously with the naked eye, the
OL,12,Fanimals often camouflaged into one
OL,13,Fanother and some would move around -
OL,14,Fmaking it difficult to spot them from
OL,15,Fa distance.
OL,17,FKevin McIlwee, Chairman of Jersey
OL,18,FMarine Conservation, explains: "What's
OL,19,Freally good is we can go over to these
OL,20,Fcolonies without disturbing them.
