OL,6,F"The thermal imaging actually picks
OL,7,Fthe pups up as white dots so we can
OL,8,Faccurately record how many we see.
OL,10,F"That's the big problem, if you try
OL,11,Fand do it from a RIB (rigid inflatable
OL,12,Fboat) you're only recording what you
OL,13,Fcan see but a lot more can be there."
OL,15,FAlong with grey seals which are rare
OL,16,Fglobally but more common around the
OL,17,FBritish Isles, Jersey's Ecrehous reef
OL,18,Fis also home to around 100 birds and
OL,19,Fmore than 400 marine species.
