OL,6,FThermal imaging is now helping to
OL,7,Fpreserve the natural diversity of the
OL,8,Fsite.
OL,10,FKevin adds: "We want to know how many
OL,11,Fseals are breeding here.
OL,13,F"We get lots of reports of them being
OL,14,Fseen but not necessarily having bred
OL,15,Fand that they're just here for
OL,16,Ffeeding. We want to know how big the
OL,17,Fcommunity is."
OL,19,FTechnology is also being used to learn
OL,20,Fmore about other animals in the area.
