OL,6,FThis year, ultrasound recordings
OL,7,Fshowed that bats make up part of the
OL,8,FEcrehous' ecosystem.
OL,10,FGregory Guida, a bat monitor, says:
OL,11,F"We didn't know whether they were here
OL,12,Fat all.
OL,14,F"The first cards that we recovered
OL,15,Fwhen we did our maintenance had four
OL,16,Fspecies on them. We've done the same
OL,17,Fin the Minquiers and there's also some
OL,18,Fbats there, it's quite exciting."
