OL,6,FHe adds that monitoring will continue
OL,7,Fso they can build up a better picture
OL,8,Fof the mammal's habits.
OL,10,FGregory explains: "We're going to do
OL,11,Fthat for a whole year, to see the
OL,12,Fpatterns when they come here and also
OL,13,Fquite interestingly whether we have
OL,14,Fmigrants."
